{"tid":241521,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日唔小心輕輕撞到的士","createTime":"2017-05-13T08:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T18:49:48.000Z","uid":97648,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4820e3b8760b1dc021b9551662ff190c0956dff6","tid":241521,"uid":97648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"利申 我係有錯我認<br />\n見到前面有架的士打咗死火燈 <br />\n諗住cut線 明明望到隔離線架車仲要一段距離先到<br />\n我個車頭出咗去cut緊㗎啦然後隔離線車咇我<br />\n我聽到咇一聲又見到佢衝埋黎 怯<br />\n本能反應扭咗左軚咁就hi凹咗架的士後側少少<br />\n佢獅子開大口本來要我賠萬二依家要我賠八千<br />\n我唔肯和解 依家報咗警<br />\n我應該點做先啱?! 好擔心覺都訓唔到 好驚佢老屈我 <br />\n我又無乜錢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/162326_a87d36c4175f0631353ef35cb86d839d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F162326_a87d36c4175f0631353ef35cb86d839d.jpg&h=ef555a30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd8e733e5391e5dcab4a78719b686811ca99ab0a","tid":241521,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"你做錯就要賠"},{"pid":"7c7671ed9fdd89339ce873c7851980f0813e51ec","tid":241521,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"賠保險有咩問題"},{"pid":"f05c8620c063d577d57c71ad210179660226c474","tid":241521,"uid":97648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做錯就要賠</blockquote><br />\n無話唔賠而係佢獅子開大口啫"},{"pid":"16acdab835950decc8e74036de57a45f50aa0cc2","tid":241521,"uid":97648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賠保險有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n少過墊底費就係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc37ce7544e361f8332c731e6db5a05c8cb7d10","tid":241521,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"撞的士唔係一千幾百搞掂架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c32f35bfba961e5b1db57c68a5ab409896ea5f5","tid":241521,"uid":97648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞的士唔係一千幾百搞掂架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個就係問題 佢依家問我拎八千我可以點"},{"pid":"27f1b495f5bde3796ea6d57ad501fa7e21e5a5bc","tid":241521,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撞的士唔係一千幾百搞掂架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個就係問題 佢依家問我拎八千我可以點</blockquote><br />\n睬佢老味<br />\nhi花小小都8k?<br />\n佢以為佢揸緊Audi ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db8cca59ee52e598f512055a59896e21a2c0b52","tid":241521,"uid":18187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"你撞的士: 一萬起跳 再打7折<br />\n的士撞你: 兄弟，小小野就算吶<br />\n<br />\n樓主唔好彩"},{"pid":"aca7bf1921d4035567e61b685f9e596076ed8910","tid":241521,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb7023b38059e910128ce3aa7a5315cdf842b41","tid":241521,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"樓主我撐你"},{"pid":"3e003dca6232238b10df086d8c6d9237d80ada5a","tid":241521,"uid":60840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f0599be4321621058e96c220faafdc727022c1","tid":241521,"uid":13157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"殺到四千先叫正常<br />\n揼返出黎都係2、3千 比多少少當飲茶"},{"pid":"7f5b5f43dd1063a79e404a8b54128ddb98b0886e","tid":241521,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:52:08.000Z","msg